Installtion Guide for MINGW compiler for Windows using Msys2

1. Download MSYS from Official Site
https://www.msys2.org/

2. After installation ,Run and Type
pacman -S mingw-w64-ucrt-x86_64-gcc

3. Update MSYS using
pacman -Syu

4. Install the Toolchain Using
pacman -S mingw-w64-x86_64-toolchain

Check gcc version on your cmd using
gcc --version

Voila! You're good to go!
